{
  "page": "Feature quote/75",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys II Targaryen\">Jaehaerys</a> once told me that madness and greatness are two sides of the same coin. every time a new <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryen</a> is born, he said, the gods toss the coin in the air, and the world holds its breath to see how it will land.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Ser Barristan Selmy</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183714\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 122/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 312/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 527/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.559      1 -total\n100.00%    4.559      1 Template:Ref\n 65.85%    3.002      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7782-0!ca